flowchart TD
    start([Start]) --> openReports[Admin or librarian opens detailed reports]
    openReports --> checkRole{Logged in as admin or librarian?}
    checkRole -->|No| denyAccess[Redirect to login or show access denied]
    denyAccess --> endNode([End])
    checkRole -->|Yes| chooseReport[Choose Book, Borrow Return, Fine, or Lost Damaged report]

    chooseReport --> chooseTimeRange[Select day, week, month, quarter, or year range]
    chooseTimeRange --> loadReportData[Load report data for selected type and range]
    loadReportData --> showReport[Display report results]
    showReport --> chooseAction{Choose action}

    chooseAction -->|Change report type| chooseReport
    chooseAction -->|Change time range| chooseTimeRange
    chooseAction -->|Export CSV| exportCsv[Generate CSV export]
    chooseAction -->|Exit| endNode

    exportCsv --> exportSuccess[Download CSV file]
    exportSuccess --> showReport
